metadata.name: Presence*
metadata.description:
Amidst the chaos of life,
We struggle and adapt.
But finding peace of mind is no easy feat,
It requires acceptance of the present, and surety that we have everything we need.

"Presence" is the response to "To a Fault" 
A Poster denoting the chaotic and difficult structures of life at times.

A practice in gratitude, and consistency as I delve into art and design through a 365 day poster challenge. (That has required a new adaptation to my daily life as I try to achieve new consistency)
